Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 去村子怎么走? - 先一直向前,然后再升.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Where is the village? - First you walk down, and then up again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}70年代末. 阿尔巴尼亚的一个村儿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The end of the 70s. A village in Albania.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}改编自真人真事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Based on actual events.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好. 学校在哪?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good day. Where's the school?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直走一段右拐, 再直走.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Just walk down a bit to the right, and then straight up again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们在那里干什么? 离开那里!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What are you doing there? Get out of there!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是新来的生物老师? 你是从地拉那来的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you the new biology teacher? Are you from Tirana?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们一直在等你.我的名字是德因.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We've been waiting for you. My name is Djin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是地理老师也临时兼任 学校长椅修理工.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm the geography teacher and ocassionally the school bench repairman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我名叫帕什克. - 这里很好,比地拉那（首都）更好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- My name is Pashk. - It's good here, better than in Tirana.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 这真好. - 这该死的锁.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- It's nice. - This damn lock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比我想象的要好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's better than I expected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生物课12点开始.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The biology lesson begins at 12PM.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有了这一区域最好教室.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You've got the best class room in the district.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}阿尔巴尼亚马列主义朋友们 要来看看.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Albanias marxist-leninistic friends are coming to have a look at it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们将其用于 全体教师会了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We use it for the faculty meetings too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你很走运. 这是给你的巨大荣誉.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You're lucky. It's a big honour for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到我办公室来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come by my office afterwards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也是,Pashk.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You too, Pashk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“根据规定和传统 这有两个新口号.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"According to the regulations and traditions here are two new slogans."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“亲爱的安德烈,你可以选择：”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Dear Andr? you can choose between:"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“美帝是一个纸老虎,” -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The American Imperialism is a Paper Tiger," -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“ - 和‘革命精神奋发向上!’.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"- and 'Get the Revolution Spirit Up!'."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是戴安娜,法语老师.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This is Diana, french teacher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你选哪个?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you chosen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你对口号没任何意见?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't you have any comments on the slogans?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想知道我们怎么弄这些口号的吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do you want to know how we make them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我以前从来没有布置过, 但我肯定我会学.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I have never laid them before, but I'm sure I will learn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Pashk将向你解释方法, 生产这些口号背后的技术.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Pashk will explain the method to you and the technology behind the production of slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}既然你是新来的,你可以选择.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Since you are new, you can choose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我选择其中之一? - 是.哪个?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I shall choose one of them? - Yes. Which one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道.他们都挺有趣.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know. They're both interesting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我同意,但两个是太多了. - 戴安娜也应有一个.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I agree, but two are too much. - And Diana shall also have one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你来决定.这不难.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Make up your mind. It's not hard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不喜欢犹豫的人.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't like people who hesitate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个是“美帝是一个纸老虎.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The first one is: "The American Imperialism is a Paper Tiger."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另一个是“革命精神奋发向上.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The other one: "Get the Revolution Spirit Up."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会是哪个?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What's it gonna be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我选与精神有关的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll take the other one, the one with the spirit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它让我更容易为 此专心致志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's easier for me to concentrate on that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看帕什克 得到了很好的导师.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I see Pashk has been a good mentor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以,这会是你的第一个口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}So, this will be your first slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戴安娜,你得到：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Diana, you get:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“美帝是一个纸老虎.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The American Imperialism is a Paper Tiger.."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你为什么生闷气? 我不明白.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Why are you sulking? I don't understand it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我理解 戴安娜同志的感受.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I understand how comrade Diana feels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她宁愿有 有个更抒情的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}She would rather have had a more lyrical slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是,党委有 决定应该怎么做.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But the party comittee have decided that this is how it should be done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我们想想, 这是做到这一点的最好办法.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And if we think, this is the best way to do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 祝你好运,安德烈. - 谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Good luck, Andr? - Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨巴夫同志是数学老师.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrade Sabaf is the math teacher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}除此之外.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Among other things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他也是村里的党委书记.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He is also the party secretary in the village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以他要负责我们所有的党务工作.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}So he's got the responsibility for us and all work for the party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你忘了你的协议!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You forgot your protocol!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要坚强,安德烈同志,坚强.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Be strong, comrade Andr? strong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恭喜!你有个良好的开端.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Congratulations. You had a good start.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你什么意思? 我对口号一无所知.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What dou you mean? I know nothing about slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是想帮助帕什克. 他有我的 .\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I just wanted to help Pashk. He have me a sign.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是个傻瓜!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What a fool!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}堕落! 这只是纯粹的报复.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Corruption! It's nothing but pure revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别摇铃了,来了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Stop ringing the bell and come in now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 午安. - 请坐下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Good day. - Please sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}美帝是一个纸老虎\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}THE AMERICAN IMPERIALISM IS A PAPER TIGER{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐下,孩子们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sit down, children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很高兴,终于 见到你了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm happy to finally have met you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我的名字是... - 安德烈\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- My name is... - Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们一起学习... - 生物!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Together we'll learn... - Biology!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈,我们用哪个口号?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr? which slogan did we get?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等一下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Wait a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许是： “革命精神奋发向上”?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Maybe it was: "Get the Revolution Spirit Up"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正确!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Correct!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的很不错.只有23个.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Really good. Only 23.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 23个什么? - 23个字母,安德烈. 真的很不错.只有23.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- 23 what? - 23 letter, Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我听说你是新来的老师.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I hear you're the new teacher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是这样.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有烟吗? 我烟草用完了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you got a cigarette? I'm out of tobacco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没有火柴.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I haven't got any matches.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有多少牲口?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}How many animals have you got?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 去年我有27个. - 现在呢?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Last year I had 27. - And now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀,我的儿子,知道. 他喜欢数数.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim, my son, knows that. He likes to count.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的名字是塞尔曼·托斯库.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}My name is Selman Tosku.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这香烟味道非常好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The cigarette tasted very good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看这里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Look here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一般般.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}So so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们出去到田里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's go out to the field.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你喜欢?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}How do you like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那是谁的口号? - 是老师米拉的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Whose slogan is that? - It's teacher M'ira's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}忘记的敌人最危险\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}THE MOST DANGEROUS ENEMY IS THE ONE THAT IS FORGOTTEN{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老师!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Teacher!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我能拿那些字母I吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Can I have the I's?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们怎么区分? - 模仿字母表.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- How are we supposed to divide the others? - After the alphabet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}给女孩们最简单的字母,把i 上的点和逗号给生病的孩子.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The easiest ones to the girls, and the dot over the i's or the commas to the sick ones.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把字母m都给好学生. 最难的是字母S.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And the m's to the good students. The hardest ones are the S's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 很难做出曲线. - 还是让你的计划好后做吧.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- It's hard to make the curves. - Then let's do it after your plans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也有一个字母.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll also have a letter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不,不! 你俯瞰这块区域.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No, no! You'll overlook the placement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果这些字母歪了, 口号将受到损害.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If the letters are crooked, the slogan will be compromised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这将是本村的耻辱!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And it will be a shame for the village!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们开始?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Shall we begin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 干得好,老师. - 谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Good work, teacher. - Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就这样. 谢谢大家.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's all. Thank you everybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}需要帮忙吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Can I help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不,没必要的. 我可以自己做到.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No, it's not necessary. I can do this on my own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在请走开!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Please. Go now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你和帕什克可以 总是扎堆.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You and Pashk could always get together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戴安娜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Diana.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“美帝是一个纸老虎”是什么意思?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What does "The American Imperialism is a Paper Tiger" mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“美帝是一个纸老虎”意思是...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The American Imperialism is a Paper Tiger" means...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们应该做到最好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That we should do our best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是你的哥哥死了吗,莱什? - 是的,萨巴夫同志,他死了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Is your brother dead, Lesh? - Yes, comrade Sabaf, he is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 愿你长寿. - 我的朋友也是.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- May you live long. - My friends too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是你的哥哥死了,莱什?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Is your brother dead, Lesh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是的,帕什克,他已经死了. - 愿你长寿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Yes, Pashk, he is dead. - May you live long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的朋友也是.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}My friends too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是你的哥哥死了,莱什?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Is your brother dead, Lesh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是的,德因,他已经死了. - 愿你长寿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Yes, Djin, he's dead. - May you live long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的朋友也是.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}My friends too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是你的哥哥死了,莱什?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Is your brother dead, Lesh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是新来的老师?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you the new teacher?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是. - 你叫什么名字?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Yes. - What's your name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的,安德烈,我的哥哥死了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, Andr? my brother is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哀悼慰问.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Condolences.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的朋友也是.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}My friends too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她恨我.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}She hates me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}算了吧.在这里最重要的是要被 拥有权力的人们喜欢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Forget it. The most important thing is to be liked by the ones who's got the power here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}特别是党.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Especially by the Party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一些事情 你必须明白.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There are some things you must understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道去年发生了什么吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do you know what happened last year?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一位校长被逮个正着 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}A headmaster was caught red-handed -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 当时他正和一个声誉不好的女老师乱搞.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- while he made love with a female teacher who had a bad reputation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这导致口号被换.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It lead to the slogans being exchanged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“国际无产阶级万岁,” 被更换为：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Long Live the Proletariat's Internationalism," was exchanged with:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“警惕,警惕,时刻警惕.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"On Guard, More on Guard, Always on Guard."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}见鬼!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Damn!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}科利,给我一个新水桶!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Koli, give me a new bucket!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}病假不少.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The sick leave is high.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拿出你的作业本. 我想看看你的功课.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Bring out your notebooks. I want to see your homework.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塔米.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Tami.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的单词变形作业在哪?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Where's your homework about metamorphose?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还没做. 我累了,安德烈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I haven't done it. I was tired, Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你呢? - 我没做.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- And you? - I didn't do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有人写作业了吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hasn't anyone made their homework?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我从口号地点步行回家 走了一个半小时.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It takes me one and a half hour to walk home from the slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你呢? - 一样.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- And you? - Same thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果只是一两个...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If it were only one, two or three...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但全班（都没写）!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But the whole class!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你觉得我该怎么办? 告诉校长?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you think I should do? Tell the headmaster?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不,安德烈.请不要! - 原谅我们这一次.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- No, Andr? please don't! - Forgive us just this one time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们用过我的好意了. 你们不是我的朋友.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You have used my kindness. You're not my friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.96,0:24:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是你们的老师, 不是你们的朋友.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm your teacher, not your friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我会告诉校长. - 不.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I'll tell the headmaster. - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我做作业了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But I did my homework.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些淘气鬼! 这是集体怠工!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Rascals! This is collective sabotage!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.76,0:25:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的.你在侮辱老师吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Really. So you're insulting the teacher?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.76,0:25:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他没有侮辱我. 他只是没有做功课.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He didn't insult me. He just didn't do his homework.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.72,0:25:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有你,是谁这么冷静?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And you, who's so calm?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也是.. 你的作业在哪?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You too.. Where's you homework?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.96,0:25:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你这小混蛋, 你没有做你的功课?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And you, little brat, haven't you done your homework?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.08,0:26:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁说的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Who said that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.52,0:26:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}站起来!站起来!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Stand up! Stand up!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.60,0:26:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}淘气鬼!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Rascals!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.88,0:26:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果这再发生,就告诉我,.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Just tell me if this happens again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.08,0:26:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢,我不这么想.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks, I don't think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.24,0:26:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这没必要.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It won't be necessary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.44,0:27:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是每个人都会去首都.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Not everybody's going to the capital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.28,0:27:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来吧. 我不走那条路.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on. I'm not going that way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走开!你这头猪!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Get lost! Pig!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们在这里不是 收集你留下的粪便.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We're not here to collect the dung you left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下午好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.16,0:28:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有烟吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you got a cigarette?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.08,0:28:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}继续.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Go on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.24,0:28:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}中国和阿尔巴尼亚是朋友, 钢的带绑在一起.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}China and Albania are friends, tied together with a band of steel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.80,0:28:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kina（欧洲部分地区对华旧称）是修正主义国家.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Kina is a revisionistic country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.16,0:29:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就够了.闭嘴.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's enough. Silence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起,我说的不对. 中国是社会主义.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry, I said wrong. China is socialistic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}苏联是修正主义.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's the Soviet Union that's revisionistic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.40,0:29:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢,坐下. 很好,很不错.你得到一个B.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you, sit down. It's good, very good. You get a B.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.76,0:29:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好,德因.这狗崽子托斯库 终于露出了本来面目!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good, Djin. This boy puppy Tosku has let the mask fall at last!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.16,0:29:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你什么意思? - 你知道我的意思.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- What dou you mean? - You know what I mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我在等你通知我们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I was waiting for you to inform us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.84,0:29:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是什么意思,萨巴夫同志?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you mean, comrade Sabaf?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.60,0:29:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天哪,今天你真幼稚.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Goodness, you're really playing naive today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:30:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果德因不希望 告诉我们发生了什么事, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If Djin doesn't want to tell us what happened, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.44,0:30:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我会.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.48,0:30:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀·托斯库 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim Tosku -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.48,0:30:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 来自本区最革命的家庭!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- comes from one of the most revolutionary families in the district!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.80,0:30:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼·托斯库和其他人喜欢他.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman Tosku and others like him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}昨天费斯汀在课堂上响亮地说, 中国是一个修正主义国家.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yesterday Festim said quite loud in the lesson that China is a revisionistic country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.76,0:30:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦,是的. 现在我知道你在说什么了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Oh, yes, that. Now I know what you're talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你误导. 我知道到底发生了什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You're misinformed. I know what really happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.72,0:30:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀·托斯库 是我最好的学生之一.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim Tosku is one of my best students.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他经常说话太快,因为 他学会用心脏做作业.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He often talks too fast because he's learned his homework by heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.68,0:30:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}替代了说苏联 是修正主义,他说的中国.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Instead of saying that the Soviet Union is revisionistic, he said China.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.92,0:30:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他瞬间改口. 他知道,他说的不对.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He corrected himself instantly. He knew that he said wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.60,0:30:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道 他来自一个可疑的家庭.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I know that he's from a doubtful family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是,即使家人不参加 全国自由运动, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But even if the family did not participate in the national freedom movement, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.56,0:31:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那男孩没有故意的行为.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- the boy did not act deliberately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的意思是他是一个好学生, 但我有不同意见.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You mean that he's a good student, but I'm of a different opinion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.80,0:31:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我经常给他困难的 字母,他应得的!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I often give him hard letters that he deserve!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.52,0:31:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另外,出了事你想给自己找借口.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Also you're trying to make excuses for what happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.24,0:31:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这对我校是一次不同寻常的 遗憾事件.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This is an extraordinary and regrettable event for our school.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.36,0:31:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我将不得不通报本地区党委.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I will have to inform the Party Comittee in the district about this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨巴夫同志,我再说一遍：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrade Sabaf, I repeat:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.48,0:31:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这仅仅是一个错误,一个失误.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It was just a mistake, an error.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.40,0:31:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种行为不是 出于政治动机.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This act was not politically motivated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.32,0:31:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要问问其他学生.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Just ask the other students.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.84,0:32:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这正是我们要做的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's exactly what we're going to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.44,0:32:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我们先来听听 费斯汀告诉我们什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But first we'll hear what Festim has to tell us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.40,0:32:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}孩子们比他们的家长更诚实-\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The children are much more honest than their parents-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.96,0:32:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 比其他伪君子更诚实.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- and other hypocrite adults.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.84,0:32:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很好.让我们干吧,萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Great. Let's do it, comerade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}之后我们在教师会议上讨论.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}After that we'll discuss this in a faculty meeting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.88,0:32:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们明天见.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll see you tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.40,0:32:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戴安娜,稍等.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Diana, wait a moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.44,0:32:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戴安娜,我给你一个建议 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Diana, let me give you an advice, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 为你自己好：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- for your own good:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.88,0:32:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别对党委书记表现出你的不信任.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do not show your distrust openly to the party secretary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但这太难以置信了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But it's incredible!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.40,0:33:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个年仅10岁的男生 说中国是修正主义, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}A small schoolboy barely 10 years old says that China is revisionistic, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.12,0:33:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 他涉嫌后援一场政治阴谋! 这真是令人难以置信.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- and he's suspected to stand behind a political conspiracy! It's unbelievable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是否难以置信, 不是我们的问题.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Unbelievable or not, it's not our problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.52,0:33:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真相早晚会出来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The truth will come out sooner or later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.84,0:33:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只关心 什么对你最适合,黛安娜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm only concerned about what's best for you, Diana.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.36,0:33:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你必须明白,这些 会耗费你很多精力.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You must understand that these things can cost you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你什么意思?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.68,0:33:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道的比我好, 可以是多么危险 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know better than me, how risky it can be -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.48,0:33:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 获得批准, 回家歇几天.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- to get permission to travel home for a few days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.40,0:33:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道是怎么回事 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know how it is -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 当你得到一个挺长的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- when you get a long slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.08,0:34:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道有一个很长的口号 是什么意思!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know what it means to have a very long slogan!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.08,0:34:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你很清楚他有多重要, 谁在这样的情况下做决定.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know very well, how important he is, who makes the decisions in cases like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你对此什么意思? - 我的意思是......我的意思.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- What do you mean with that? - I mean... I mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.16,0:35:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来吧,费斯汀.赶紧的. 全体教师正在等你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on, Festim. Hurry. The whole faculty is waiting for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.72,0:35:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀,过来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.84,0:35:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这真荒谬.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This is absurd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.52,0:35:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你能告诉萨巴夫老师和我们 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Could you tell teacher Sabaf and us -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.72,0:35:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 谁在家里告诉你的 中国是一个修正主义国家?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- who told you at home that China is a revisionistic country?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.32,0:35:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无论是在家还是其他地方 都没人告诉我.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Nobody told me, neither at home nor in other places.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.24,0:35:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.88,0:36:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在这里没人要伤害你. 只要看看我有多好我现在.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Nobody here means to hurt you. Just look at how nice I am right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.00,0:36:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你父亲和你什么事都没有. 只要告诉我们谁告诉你的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Nothing will happen to your father or you. Just tell us who told you it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.24,0:36:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是说,哪本书写着, 中国是个社会主义国家.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I just said what the book said, that China is a socialistic country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.72,0:36:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们不要求你背书.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We did not ask you to recite the book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你必须告诉我们谁 让你在课上说的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You must tell us who made you say that in the lesson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.04,0:36:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么德因老师 说你纠正自己?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Why does teacher Djin say that you corrected yourself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.96,0:36:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没有说! 我没说......\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I didn't say it! I didn't say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.88,0:36:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没说......\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I didn't say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.76,0:36:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在,你最好表现出一定的合作意愿!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Now you better show some will to cooperate!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.08,0:36:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说实话,我并不反对 你或你的父亲.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}To be honest I have nothing against you or your father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.32,0:36:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是,谁教的你父亲 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But who teached your father that -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 苏联是 社会主义......呃......资本主义?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- the soviet union is socialistic... uh... capitalistic?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.56,0:36:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 修正主义,萨巴夫同志. - 当然.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Revisionistic, comrade Sabaf. - Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.64,0:37:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说什么?现在告诉我们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you say? Tell us now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.56,0:37:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你没有赢得什么,萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You've got nothing to win by forcing it out, comrade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.24,0:37:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他什么也没承认, 而我们正在浪费时间.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He's got nothing to confess, and we're wasting our time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.76,0:37:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冷静,冷静...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Easy, easy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.32,0:37:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以用其他方法!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I could use other methods!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.08,0:37:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀·托斯库.小心.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim Tosku. Be careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.88,0:37:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你和你父亲非常清楚 萨巴夫同志是谁.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You and your father know very well who comrade Sabaf is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.12,0:37:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你的家人知道 巡逻车到这里来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I know your family knows the patrol car that comes here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.40,0:37:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叫你父亲明天和我在 办公室明天见面.现在离开这里!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Ask your father to meet me in my office tomorrow. Now get out of here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.44,0:37:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我的错,萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's my fault, comerade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.24,0:38:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没说清楚 政治方面在事件发生的时间.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I was not clear over the political aspects at the time of the event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.72,0:38:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦,我很清楚当这些 修正主义份子藏在哪.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Oh, I know very well where these revisionistic hares hide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.48,0:38:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.68,0:38:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}费斯汀?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Festim?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.12,0:38:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我告诉你什么? - 没什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- What did I tell you? - Nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.68,0:38:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 没什么重要的事. - 那你为什么哭?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Nothing important. - Then why are you crying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}各位同事,萨巴夫同志 是从党委回来, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Colleagues, comrade Sabaf is back from the party comittee, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.96,0:38:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 谁给了新口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- who's given new slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.88,0:39:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}亲爱的同志们,亲爱的同事们：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Dear comrades, dear colleagues:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.88,0:39:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在一个半月后. 党中央政治局一位委员 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}In one and a half months. a member of the party -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.04,0:39:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 将乘车在高速公路上 沿着我们村子驶过.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- will drive by on the highway that runs along our village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.48,0:39:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我目前无法告诉你们是谁.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I cannot currently tell you who it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.92,0:39:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出于安全原因.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Security reasons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.52,0:39:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许他会在我们村停下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Maybe he'll stop by in our village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.96,0:39:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此,我们将搞一个 口号的活动.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Therefore we will start a campaign to renew the slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.96,0:39:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们开始. 德因,这次我们给大家：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's begin. Djin, this time we give you:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.28,0:39:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“中国阿尔巴尼亚友谊万岁.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Long Live the Chinese-Albanian friendship."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.04,0:39:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢你,校长.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you, headmaster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.00,0:39:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}德因,-\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Djin, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你也要负责 公路沿线的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- you'll also be in charge for the work with the slogans along the highway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.04,0:39:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那显示出“恩维尔·霍查”（总书记） 字母要越大越好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There it will read "Enver Hoxha", with as large letters as possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.12,0:39:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}军队会帮助你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The army will help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.28,0:40:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}帕什克,你负责口号： “工人阶级的党万岁.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Pashk, you got: "Long Live the Worker's Party."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.08,0:40:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我感谢党.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I thank the party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.60,0:40:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr? -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.16,0:40:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你的新口号是：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- your new slogan is:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.20,0:40:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要让工作,思想和生活 充满革命的意识.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Work, think and live like a revolutionary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.72,0:40:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在轮到你,黛安娜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And now it's your turn, Diana.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.40,0:40:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为表扬你承担义务, 我们给你口号：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Because we praise your commitment, we give you:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.24,0:40:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“加强无产阶级专政, 加强社会民主主义.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The Stronger the Dictature of the Proletariate, the Stronger the Social Democracy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.04,0:40:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就知道.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I knew it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起,你是怎么知道的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Excuse me, what did you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.72,0:40:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你喜欢给 我很长的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That you enjoy to give me mile long slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.52,0:40:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}告诉我,同志,你这 公报私仇要持续多久?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Tell me, comrade, how long will you carry on this personal revenge of yours?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.04,0:41:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以个人目的使用口号是耻辱.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's a shame using slogans as personal objects.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.40,0:41:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}戴安娜,这是党委的 决定,不是我.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Diana, it's the party comittee that decides, not me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.48,0:41:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且为什么我会想要报复你? 你有料反对口号?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And why would I want to take any revenge on you? Have you got anything against slogans?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.60,0:41:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我向大家强调 这个口号 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I emphasize for everyone that this slogan -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.88,0:41:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是第七届党代会定的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- was made on the 7th Party Congress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.32,0:41:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 同志,我有个建议. - 什么?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Comrade, I have a suggestion. - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会用我的“中国 - 阿尔巴尼亚” 口号与戴安娜的交换.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll exchange my "Chinese-Albanian" slogan with Diana's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.96,0:41:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别问了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's out of question!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们不会坐在这为口号讨价还价 只因有人突发奇想!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We will not sit here and bargain with slogans just because someone has a whim!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.24,0:41:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 但是... - 没有但是!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- But... - No buts!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.72,0:41:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 只是个建议. - 没有建议或抗议!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- It was just a suggestion. - No suggestions or protests!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.28,0:41:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些口号是我们的政治任务.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The slogans are our political tasks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.96,0:42:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是如果有人反对口号, 事情的性质就变了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But if someone is against slogans, thing's will change!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.84,0:42:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}米拉,因为你的口号依然 很有创意,我们不会改变它：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}M'ira, since your slogan still is of current interest, we won't change it:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.20,0:42:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“忘记的敌人最危险.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The Most Dangerous Enemy is the One That Is Forgotten."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.56,0:42:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}非常感谢,同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks a lot, comrade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.80,0:42:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}扎娜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Zana.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.36,0:42:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“人民崛起,党在前进.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The People Rise, the Party Forward."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.56,0:42:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢,同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks, comrade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就这样.谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's all. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.44,0:43:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别想啦.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't think about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.68,0:43:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会帮你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.80,0:43:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以一起做. 或者我自己来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We could do it together. Or I could do it on my own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.64,0:43:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只会花我两个星期天.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It will only take me two Sundays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.36,0:43:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks a lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.72,0:43:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 晚安,安德烈. - 晚安.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- God night, Andr? - God night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}赶快!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.00,0:43:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}赶快!抓紧!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on! Hurry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.72,0:44:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你有一张图片? - 把它向左一点.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Have you got a picture? - Turn it a little to the left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.20,0:44:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}欢迎.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.36,0:44:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 祝贺这新电视. - 谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Congratulations to the new TV. - Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.28,0:44:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祝贺.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Congratulations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是我,安德烈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's just me, Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.44,0:45:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放羊的塞尔曼·托斯库, 从雨中来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Goat farmer Selman Tosku, comes out of the rain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.68,0:45:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你来这里不是为说这个?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You're not coming here just to say that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.68,0:45:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我来请你为我 给政府写信.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I come to ask you to write a letter to the government for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.08,0:45:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不会读也不会写.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I can't read nor write.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.24,0:45:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我活得很可怜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I live very poor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.28,0:45:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我住的小屋随时都会倒塌 砸在我头上.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The cabin I'm living in is threatening to fall apart over my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冬天,我的儿子费斯汀 去朋友那里一起住.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}In the winter, my son Festim, sleeps at friends of his.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.44,0:45:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And you know what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.76,0:45:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在雨天我只要躺下睡觉, 雨水就掉在我鼻子上.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}One rainy day when I lay sleeping, it began to drop on my nose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.68,0:46:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我总以为有人在舔我, 或者冲着我撒尿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I thought that someone was licking me, or maybe pissing on me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.96,0:46:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去和村委会谈谈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Talk to the village council about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.08,0:46:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你认为谁会听我的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Who do you think will listen to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.12,0:46:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会很喜欢住在 合住的房子里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I would really like to live in one of the cooperative houses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.44,0:46:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有别人,邻居,儿童...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There's people, neighbors, children...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.64,0:46:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一个地方,我可以说.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}A place where I can talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.44,0:46:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进来,学校的门是放着的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come in. The door to the school is open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.28,0:47:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐到火炉.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sit down at the stove.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.72,0:47:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.88,0:47:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你可以写.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You can write.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.36,0:47:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要忘记告诉 他们漏雨的情况.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't forget to tell them about the leakage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.24,0:47:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然.但现在让我写.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Of course not. But let me write now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.68,0:47:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请你让我写?相信我. 我不会忘记漏雨的事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Will you please let me write? Trust me. I won't forget about the leakage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.20,0:47:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我相信你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I trust you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.08,0:48:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.76,0:48:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许你最好别提漏雨.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Maybe you'd better not mention the leakage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.12,0:48:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看上去微不足道.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It could seem petty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.08,0:48:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}擦掉漏雨的内容.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Wipe that about the leakage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.76,0:48:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不写漏雨,好吧?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I won't write about the leakage, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.72,0:48:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼,我写完了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman, I'm finished.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.04,0:48:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在你把它放进信封前, 能读给我听?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Before you put it in the envelope, could you read it to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.48,0:48:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“申请.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Application."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.04,0:48:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我出生在这个村庄 一直住在一个小屋里.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"I'm born in this village and have always lived in the same cabin."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我的生活没什么可说的,-”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"As there isn't much to say about my life, -"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.12,0:49:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“- 我直入主题.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"- I will go straight to the main cause."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.28,0:49:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我一直诚实地工作.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"I've always worked honestly."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.60,0:49:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“还是修不起我快塌了的小屋 -”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Still I cannot afford to repair my cabin, which could fall apart -"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“- 直到现在.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"- any time now."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.20,0:49:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.20,0:49:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不,没什么.心难受. -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No, nothing. It hurts. -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.96,0:49:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 继续,都读了. - 但是你怎么了?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Continue, read it all. - But what is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.88,0:49:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}心难受 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It hurts -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.32,0:49:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 听别人谈论我的生活.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- hearing others talk about my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.88,0:49:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 伤害了谁? - 我自己!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Hurts who? - Myself!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.52,0:49:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把你的信明天发到村里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Take your letter and send it to the village tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.24,0:49:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不,读到底.我会的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No, read the end. I'll do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.24,0:49:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“充满希望...”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Hopeful..."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.76,0:50:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了,塞尔曼?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What is it, Selman?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.96,0:50:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要表现得像个大人!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Behave like a grownup man!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.28,0:50:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这信送到后,你认为他们会给 我一个新房子吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do you think they'll give me a new house after this letter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.24,0:50:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.60,0:50:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈,请.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr? please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.64,0:50:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再读一遍. 我想听听你写了什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Read it one more time. I want to hear what you've written.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.76,0:50:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 当然,别再流眼泪了! - 我只是想再听一次.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Sure, but no more tears! - I just want to hear it one more time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.80,0:50:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我出生在这个村庄 一直住在一个小屋里.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"I'm born in this village and have always lived in the same cabin."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我的生活没什么可说的,我直入主题.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"As there isn't much to say about my life, I will go straight to the main cause.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.44,0:50:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我一直诚实地工作.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"I've always worked honestly."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.80,0:50:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“还是修不起我快塌了的小屋 -”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Still I cannot afford to repair my cabin, which could fall apart -"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.24,0:50:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“- 直到现在.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"- any time now."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.20,0:50:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“充满希望并相信党,-”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Hopeful and with trust to the party, -"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.16,0:51:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“- 我希望可以解决 我的问题.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"- I hope my problem can be solved."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.72,0:51:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}晚安.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.16,0:51:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别问我了. 我不会再读这封信了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't ask me about it. I won't read the letter one more time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.68,0:51:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已经很晚了. 回家睡觉去.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's late. Go home and go to bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.40,0:51:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这不是我来这里的原因.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's not the reason why I'm here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.84,0:51:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道我为什么回来?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do you know why I came back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.28,0:51:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是想,怎么能 没感谢你就离开?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I just thought, how could I leave without thanking you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.72,0:51:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你为我做了这么多.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You've done so much for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.16,0:51:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以回报你什么?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What can I give you in return?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.08,0:51:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}西红柿?板栗?大蒜?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Tomatoes Chestnut? Garlic?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.84,0:52:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我这么做不是为西红柿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I didn't do it for tomatoes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.72,0:52:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这没什么. 我只是写下你告诉我的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It was nothing. I just wrote down what you told me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.60,0:52:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我想给你些东西.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But I want to give you something for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.56,0:52:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好,给我些大蒜吧. - 我自己去拿.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- OK, then give me some garlic. - I'll bring it myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.56,0:52:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很抱歉我的行为.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And I'm sorry for my behaviour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.32,0:52:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}晚安.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.40,0:52:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是谁呀? - 开门,是我!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Who is it? - Unlock, it's me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.56,0:52:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 又是你!这次又是什么? - 我带来了大蒜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- You again! What is it now? - I come with garlic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在这个时候!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}In this hour!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.16,0:52:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 也许一直等到明天. - 你猜我还有什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Maybe it could have waited until tomorrow. - Guess what more I have with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.52,0:53:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 梅酒,也许? - 正确.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Raki, maybe? - Correct.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.60,0:53:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢,我真的很需要.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks, I really needed that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.88,0:53:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尝一下!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Taste it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.20,0:53:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Very good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.64,0:53:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不,不...\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No, no...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不会再读了这封信.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I won't read the letter again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.56,0:53:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯,我想我不该强迫你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, I guess I shouldn't force you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.24,0:53:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是,我们别争了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But let's not argue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.68,0:53:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我只是来给你梅酒. - 我明白.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I just came to give you the raki. - I understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.60,0:53:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}晚安.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.72,0:53:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一起团结工作 加强同志友爱.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Working together strengthens the camaraderie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.32,0:54:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}亲爱的同学们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Dear students.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.44,0:54:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}亲爱的老师们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Dear teachers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.52,0:54:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我代表党 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}On account of the Party -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.04,0:54:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 由衷地感谢你们完成这些口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- I would like to thank you for the work you've done with the slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.20,0:54:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这一圈就这么多.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's all in this round.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.44,0:55:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}昨天我发现有些石头失踪.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yesterday I saw that the e's were missing. Some stones are missing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.68,0:55:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那些石头自己移动. - 我很生气!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Stones moving themselves. - I get mad!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.48,0:55:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 医生们称之为压力. - 我已经为口号工作了17年!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- The doctors call it stress. - I've worked with slogans for 17 years!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.28,0:55:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 有没有消息? - 没什么.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Any news? - Not much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.76,0:55:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天气真好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The weather's nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.52,0:55:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你今天下午有课吗? - 没有.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Are you teaching this afternoon? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.32,0:55:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们应该走到口号那儿? - 我三天前在那里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Should we walk over to the slogans? - I was there three days ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.72,0:55:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然,如果你这么说.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Sure, if you say so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.12,0:56:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}OK.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.20,0:57:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你抽烟吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Do you smoke?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.68,0:57:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}偶尔.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Now and then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.76,0:57:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我喜欢因为它 让我头晕目眩.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I like it because it makes me dizzy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.60,0:58:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}政治局的委员 将到这停下, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The members of the politburo will stop by here, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.24,0:58:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 还有这里, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- and here, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.16,0:58:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 前方口号： “党是幸福之父.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- in front of the slogan: "The Party is the Father of Happiness."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.32,0:58:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.56,0:58:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你身后没关门? - 这不是我来这的原因.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Don't you close your door after you? - That's not the reason why I'm here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.32,0:58:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我的口号被毁了. - 先关上门.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- It's the destroyed slogan of mine. - Close the door anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.04,0:58:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是不是有人看到? - 没有.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Did someone see you? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.20,0:59:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}扎碧特,-\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Zabit, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.00,0:59:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 农业合作社今年产量如何?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- how was the output of the cooperative this year?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.28,0:59:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真糟!每公顷两吨.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Terrible! Two tons per hectare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.68,0:59:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这并不可怕. 就像各地一样.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That's not terrible. It was like that everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.40,0:59:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每公顷2.2吨.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}2,2 tons per hectare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.40,1:00:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你能对一个只想着女人的\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What could you expect with a cooperative leader -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.40,1:00:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 农业合作社领导指望什么?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- who only thinks about ladies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.88,1:00:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你见过扎娜的儿子吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you seen Zana's son?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.92,1:00:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他喜欢吹领导的鼻子!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He's like blown out of the nose of the leader!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.92,1:00:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是怎么回事?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What's going on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.64,1:00:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼·托斯库!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman Tosku!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.92,1:00:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我以人民的名义逮捕你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I arrest you in the name of the people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.68,1:01:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.52,1:01:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}今天我们聚集在这里揭露 人民公敌：塞尔曼·托斯库.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We have gathered here today to reveal an enemy of the people: Selman Tosku.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.04,1:01:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他来自本地区一个最反动的家庭.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He comes from one of the most reactionary families in the district.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.88,1:01:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们了解他.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know him well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.48,1:01:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是他,塞尔曼 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's he, Selman, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.52,1:01:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 他机关算尽反对我们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- who's thought out an advanced way to fight us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.32,1:01:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他破坏了我们的口号 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He destroys our slogans, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.92,1:01:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 孩子们热情辛苦工作的成果.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- the ones that the children have laid down with hard work and love.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.40,1:01:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些口号蒙蔽塞尔曼.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}These slogans have blinded Selman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.16,1:01:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}认真听好,塞尔曼·托斯库.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Listen real good, Selman Tosku.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使在毒蛇的嘴里 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Even in the mouth of a serpent -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.00,1:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们也会找到你!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- we would have found you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.44,1:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尊敬的首长,-\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Your honour, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.44,1:02:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你没有证据审判我.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- you judge me without reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.88,1:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是无辜的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm innocent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.32,1:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没有做任何事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I haven't done anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.60,1:02:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我从来没有碰过那些口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I never touched the slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.64,1:02:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尊敬的首长,我能说些什么吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Your honour, may I say something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.80,1:02:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.04,1:02:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我了解塞尔曼.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I know Selman well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.88,1:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他可能是个贫穷的牧羊人, 但他是个好人.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He may be a poor goat farmer, but he's a good man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.64,1:02:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他不能读写 他不能数他的山羊.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He can't read or write and he can not count his goats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.64,1:02:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他甚至不知道 口号什么意思.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He doesn't even know what the slogans mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.08,1:02:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们缺少他的动机.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}They lack meaning to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.32,1:02:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么能判决 一个文盲 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}How can you judge an analphabet -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.24,1:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 仅为了一些和他无关的事?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- for an act that doesn't mean anything to him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.68,1:03:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼·托斯库 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman Tosku -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.24,1:03:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 一个文盲 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- is so much an analphabet -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.64,1:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 他破坏了 米拉的口号：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- that he sabotaged the slogan of M'ira's:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.64,1:03:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“忘记的敌人最危险.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"The Most Dangerous Enemy Is the One That Is Forgotten."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.04,1:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}塞尔曼·托斯库,谢谢你 教我们的.你说得太对了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Selman Tosku, thank you for what you've teached us. You're so right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.48,1:03:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们永远不会忘记你!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We will never forget you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.44,1:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}至于你,安德烈 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}As for you, Andr? -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.52,1:03:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我能说的是, 你还很年轻.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- all I can say is that you're still very young.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.64,1:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一些事情你不明白.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There are some things you don't not understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.36,1:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是,你将会学到 别介入别人的工作!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But you will learn eventually to not mind others businesses!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.16,1:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把他带走.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Take him away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.20,1:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.24,1:04:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里将有一个海报： “阿尔巴尼亚 - 坚如磐石”.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}There will be a poster reading: "Albania - The Granite Rock".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.00,1:04:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那边,在河边： “恩维尔的党”.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And over there, at the riverside: "Enver Party".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.12,1:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把那该死的发动机关掉!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Stop that goddamned motor!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.72,1:04:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我关掉它,它不会再次启动.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If I stop it, it won't start again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.88,1:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是个完美的地方 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's a perfect place -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.92,1:05:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 对停车来说.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- for the car to stop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.08,1:05:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要忘记,人们应该 站在道路两侧.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't forget that people should stand at both sides of the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.48,1:05:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望他们会开车进村! 我们必须为任何事情做好准备.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I hope they'll drive into the village! We must be prepared for anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.84,1:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们总结一下.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's summarize.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.60,1:05:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“阿尔巴尼亚人民万岁.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Long Live the Albanian People."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.48,1:05:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“无产阶级专政万岁, 团结稳定坚如磐石.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Long Live the Dictature of the Proletariat, Steady as the Primary Rock."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.08,1:05:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他当然会握住我的手 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And he will of course shake my hand -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.92,1:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 并用他的胳膊搂住我. 他还会做什么!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- and put his arm around me. What else could he do!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.96,1:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们去小学,去我们这一区 的边界找莱什.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's got o the small school, to Lesh in the outskirts of our district.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.76,1:05:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在世界尽头!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}At the end of the world!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.16,1:06:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“越南将会获胜”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"VIETNAM WILL WIN"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.12,1:06:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没想到在这里见到你,萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I wasn't expecting to see you here, comrade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.08,1:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志,这是我的荣幸.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrade, the pleasure is all mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.52,1:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Greetings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.04,1:06:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 进来. - 我们进来工作的相关业务,莱什.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Come in. - We come in work related business, Lesh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.40,1:06:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起, 但今天的教育结束了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry, but the education is over for today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.32,1:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有什么不对的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Is something wrong?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.64,1:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的,莱什.你的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, Lesh. Your slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.92,1:06:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 什么?“越南将会获胜”? - 是的,莱什.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- What? "Vietnam Will Win"? - Yes, Lesh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.28,1:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}越南战争已经结束10年了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The Vietnam war ended 10 years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.08,1:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我简直不敢相信!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I can't believe it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.52,1:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁赢了?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Who won?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.76,1:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}问题是,你的 口号已经过时了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The problem is that your slogan is obsolete.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.56,1:07:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了,莱什?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Has something happened, Lesh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.36,1:07:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}越南.是北越赢了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Vietnam. It was The North Vietnam who won.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.84,1:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}越南已经胜利了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Vietnam has won!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.52,1:07:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仁慈的祝福,越南赢了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Goodness gracious, Vietnam won!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.64,1:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们赢了!感谢上帝.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}They won! Thank God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.52,1:07:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我每晚都祈祷越南会取胜. 他们真是些狡猾的小家伙.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I prayed every night that the Vietnamese would win. They're dodgy little fellows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.24,1:07:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的口号必须被马上毁掉.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Your slogan must be destroyed immidiately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.24,1:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}莱什,我们是老朋友了,对吧?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Lesh, we're old friends, aren't we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.60,1:07:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们一起在村里下棋.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We've played chess together in the village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.08,1:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我从没想过我会走这么远.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I never thought I would have to go to these lenghts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.28,1:08:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我必须报告给全体教师 这是一种意识形态的问题.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll have to report it to the faculty as an ideological matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.16,1:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这真是不可原谅,莱什, 我甚至可以认真地说!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's really unforgivable, Lesh, I would even say serious!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.56,1:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我花了很久才弄好口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But I got it a long time ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.88,1:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在你来到这里之前,同志!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Long before you came here, comrade!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.88,1:08:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}试着去理解!你跟不上时代了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Try to understand! You're not following the news of the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以留住它作为 历史的记忆.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We could keep it like a historical memory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.88,1:08:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对,就是这样!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, exactly!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.68,1:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已经够了! 马上拆除这个口号!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Enough already! Remove this slogan immidiately!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.48,1:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}莱什,听着.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Lesh, listen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.52,1:08:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不得不在教师会议 上提及此事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll have to bring this up on the faculty meeting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.44,1:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你不会生我的气吧? - 不,没关系这是很好的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- You won't be mad at me? - No. It's good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.32,1:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.20,1:09:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么,莱什. 告诉我们发生了什么事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Well, Lesh. Tell us what happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.20,1:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很抱歉,但你是什么意思?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry, but what do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.28,1:09:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么?告诉我们为什么你 的口号还在.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What? Tell us why your slogan is still there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.84,1:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们来完成这件事.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's finish this matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.20,1:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你把纸条拿反了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You're holding the paper upside down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.36,1:10:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.60,1:10:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.20,1:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}党和\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The Party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.84,1:10:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人民\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The People.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.28,1:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只服从党的指示.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I only followed the orders from the Party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.76,1:10:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那之后,没有人告诉 我要改变口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And after that no one has asked me to change slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.00,1:10:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我和我的学生们已尽可能 让口号保持良好的状态.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I and my students have done our best to keep it in good shape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.84,1:10:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.96,1:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们唯一可以责怪莱什的, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The only thing we can blame Lesh for, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.12,1:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是他对世界各地的 革命胜利缺乏兴趣.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- is his deficient interest for the success of the revolution around the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.40,1:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果中央政治局的委员 看到这口号会怎么想?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What would the member of the politburo have thinked if he saw the slogan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.20,1:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我同意.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I agree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.76,1:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但现在我的意思是 莱什需要一个新口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But now I mean that Lesh needs a new slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.28,1:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}唯一的问题是我们不能 向党中央求教.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The only problem is we can't ask for advice from the Party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.20,1:11:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萨巴夫同志,我建议 给他一个简短的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrade Sabaf, I suggest we give him a short slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.08,1:11:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他住的偏远口号不强制.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Besides he lives so far away that a slogan is not compulsory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.04,1:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是什么意思,帕什克?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What do you mean, Pashk?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.72,1:11:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你我都知道 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know as much as I do -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.60,1:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那些资本主义国家总是嘲弄越南.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- that the capitalistic countries always have played with Vietnam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.08,1:11:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}莱什,毁掉那口号! 让我们完成这件事!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Lesh, destroy the slogan! Let's finish this matter!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.08,1:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们,我毕生忠实地为这口号工作.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrades, I've worked faithfully all my life with that slogan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.48,1:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有人会怀疑你的忠实.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}No one doubts that you've handled in good faith.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.40,1:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但这个口号已经 10年了,太旧了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But the slogan is 10 years too old!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.32,1:11:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那就给我一个现代的! - 你在世界尽头,我们给你什么呢?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- So just give me a more modern one! - What could we give you on the end of the world?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.32,1:11:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无论你想要什么,只要 包括越南这个词.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Whatever you want, as long as the word Vietnam is included{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:12:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们有孩子们在等待. 我们不能在这呆一夜.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}We've got children waiting. We can't stay here all night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.32,1:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果莱什想要一个口号 包括单词越南, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If Lesh want's a slogan with Vietnam in it, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.92,1:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“射击,越南,射击,指挥你的炮塔 向着所有的和平谈判.“\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"Shoot, Vietnam, Shoot. Direct Your Cannons Towars All Peace Negotiations."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.60,1:12:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的口号会是什么?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What will your slogan be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.56,1:12:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.04,1:12:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还没决定.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's not decided yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.36,1:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结尾升调吗, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}High heels or not, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.88,1:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 在这被遗忘的村里 没人注意到我.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- no one notices me in this forgotten village anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.84,1:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你,那的!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You there!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.92,1:14:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老师没告诉你 穿上最好的衣服吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Didn't the teacher ask you to take your best clothes on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.44,1:14:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是什么洞? 你的脚趾都露出来了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What's this hole? Your toes are sticking out!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.00,1:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就这一双鞋.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't have any other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.88,1:14:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你,那的!不要只是坐在那里. 到路上来.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You there! Don't just sit there. Come over to the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.04,1:14:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也是. 每个人都上马路.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You too. Everyone over to the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.32,1:14:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志,把所有人 转移到另一侧.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrade, move someone over to the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.56,1:15:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}赶快! 看上去多几分热情.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on! Look a little more enthusiastic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.24,1:15:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恩维尔的党!恩维尔的党!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Enver Party! Enver Party!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.64,1:15:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}阿尔巴尼亚 坚如磐石\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}ALBANIA THE GRANITE ROCK{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.92,1:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他来了!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He's coming!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.84,1:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恩维尔的党!恩维尔的党!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Enver Party! Enver Party!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.80,1:16:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}持续抵抗,越南\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}HOLD STAND, VIETNAM{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.40,1:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr? -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.68,1:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 萨巴夫同志和我想到了 画在墙上的口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- comrade Sabaf and I thought about painting a slogan on the wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.00,1:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你被赋予画它的荣誉.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You've been given the honour of painting it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.24,1:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这口号是： “无产阶级专政万岁.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The slogan is as follows: "Long Live the Dictature of the Proletariat."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.08,1:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有一件事,安德烈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And another thing, Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.88,1:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}校长和我 都非常关注.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The headmaster and I are very concerned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.76,1:17:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最近你和戴安娜的行为 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Recently your and Diana's behaviour has -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.92,1:17:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 令人关注.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- awoken concern.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.96,1:17:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在村民们眼中不是个好模范.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You've not been a good role model in the eyes of the village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.80,1:17:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你很清楚,党 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You know very well that the Party -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.12,1:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 考虑到教师的道德是圣洁的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- considers a teachers moral to be holy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.12,1:17:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此,我们建议区教委 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Therefore we have suggested to the districts education comittee -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.16,1:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 将戴安娜会被调到 另一个村子.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- that Diana's transfered to another village.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.88,1:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然很远.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Far away, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.88,1:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样一来,你会更在乎 你在学校的事业.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}That way, you will care more about your school undertakings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.08,1:17:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}特别是口号的工作.同意?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Especially in the work with the slogans. Agreed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.24,1:17:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.48,1:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}阳台上的孩子\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}A child on a balcony{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.88,1:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把花扔向头盔\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}is throwing flowers down on the helmets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.68,1:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}齐步行军前进\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}forward march{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.52,1:18:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}刺刀都在闪耀.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}the bayonets are shining.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.68,1:18:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坚持,老师!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hang on, teacher!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.52,1:19:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}赶快!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Hurry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.84,1:19:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从那下来!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Get down from there!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.72,1:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.32,1:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}党和人民是因为你 才开这次会的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The party and the people are having this meeting only because of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.52,1:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你绘制口号是用手还是用脚?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Did you paint the slogan with your hands or with your feet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.32,1:19:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很有趣.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Very fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.96,1:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}党和人民 很想知道 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The party and the people would very much want to know -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.40,1:19:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 谁让你那样画口号的?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- who asked you to paint the slogan that way?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.80,1:19:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们,我很抱歉那个错误.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry about the faults, comrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.68,1:19:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没从任何人得到指示, 萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I haven't got orders from anyone, comrade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.04,1:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我尽可能让口号好看.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I did my best to make the slogan look good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.16,1:20:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但它并没有变得好看 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But it was didn't turn out very well -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.40,1:20:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 因为墙是扭曲的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- because the wall was warped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.96,1:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜托!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Please!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.12,1:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果你只谈墙 和路径,我们永远都没完!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}If you only talk about walls and paths, we'll never finish!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.32,1:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你的意思是什么原因?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}So what do you mean is the reason?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.28,1:20:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以告诉你们.同志们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I can tell you that. Comrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.48,1:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这不仅仅是 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This isn't just about -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.00,1:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 安德烈画口号 没有必要的激情.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Andr?painting the slogan without the necessary passion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.12,1:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}问题比这更严重.安德烈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The problem runs deeper than that. Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.56,1:20:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他刚来时,就给塞尔曼·托斯库烟.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}From the moment he arrived, he gave cigarettes to Selman Tosku.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.16,1:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他成为了他的朋友, 在法庭上捍卫他.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He became his friend and defended him in the court.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.68,1:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而这还不是全部!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And that's not all!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.76,1:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}党中央政治局委员驶过时, 他没有拍手鼓掌!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}When the member of the politburo drove by, he didn't clap his hands!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.52,1:20:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的,萨巴夫同志. 你误导.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, comrade Sabaf. You're misinformed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.72,1:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯,是的,你鼓掌了. 但还是不够的热情!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Well yes, you applaused. But it wasn't enthusiastic enough!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.24,1:21:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但最糟糕的事是偷着和法语老师调情.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But the worst thing is the secret flirting with the french teacher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.00,1:21:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是他!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.56,1:21:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.72,1:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrades, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.88,1:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 这正是人民公敌的行为!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- that's exactly how an enemy of the people behaves!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.96,1:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的,一个人民的敌人!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, an enemy of the people!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.56,1:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冷静,萨巴夫同志.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Take it easy, comrade Sabaf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.56,1:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不是说要减轻他的责任, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I do not mean to lessen his slip-ups, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.12,1:21:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 但让我们和平安静地看问题.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- but let us look at the problem in peace and quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.12,1:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安德烈.你可以离开我们,直到 党在这个问题上做出决定.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Andr? you may leave us until the Party has decided in the matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.84,1:22:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很担心你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I was worried for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.88,1:22:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我已经等很久了.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I've been waiting long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.08,1:22:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这一次党选择宽容.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}This time the Party chose to be indulgent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.60,1:22:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你下放到农业合作社 去劳动6个月 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You escape with six months of hard labour -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.96,1:22:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 隆姆同志在那是领导.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- in the cooperative where comrade Lume is the leader.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.08,1:23:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 萝拉. - 老师!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Lola. - Teacher!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.56,1:23:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你累吗?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you tired?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.24,1:23:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在,我们用砖块写口号. 这很容易!\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Now we write all the slogans with bricks. It's much easier!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.28,1:23:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但还是要一砖一砖地摆.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But it's still brick after brick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.52,1:23:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在走吧.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Let's go now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.64,1:23:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}贝斯姆和艾斯特勒夫, 你俩装载拖拉机.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Besim and Estref, you load the tractor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.24,1:23:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们开始收庄稼. 安德烈.你跟着别人做.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}You begin to reap. Andr? you follow the others.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.80,1:24:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看你的这双手不是劳作用的, 而是为享受用的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}These hands of yours are not made for work, but for pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.24,1:25:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他完成了所有的工作, 他做工非常勤奋.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He's done all the tasks he was asked to do with great diligence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.04,1:25:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他帮助了我们读懂党的颂歌.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}He helped us to read the Party Song.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.32,1:25:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还能说什么?帮帮我, 同志们.我说得对吧?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}What more can I say? Help me, comrades. Am I right, or?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.64,1:25:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是,你是对的. 他勤奋工作.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes, you're right. He's worked diligently.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.56,1:25:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且他没有往后站.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}And he didn't stand back physically.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.24,1:25:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同志们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Comrades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.28,1:25:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我诚心诚意感谢你们.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}I thank you of all my heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.00,1:25:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我给你们的口号是：\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The slogan I give you is:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.16,1:25:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“稻堆堆得圆又圆,社员堆稻上了天. 撕片白云擦擦汗,凑上太阳抽根烟.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"May the Campaign of Sowing and Harvesting be Crowned with Luck."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.56,1:26:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很适合在合作社的工作.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It fits the work you did in the cooperative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.04,1:26:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有一件事,安德烈.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}One more thing, Andr?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.16,1:26:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最近 -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Recently -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.76,1:26:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们一直在用砖头 而不是石头.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- we've been using bricks instead of rocks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.84,1:26:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样更有利于实用和美观.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It gives many practical and aesthetic benefits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.68,1:26:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不再需要把岩石刷白,-\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}It's no longer necessary to bleach the rocks, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.56,1:26:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 下雨和动物们 再也不能破坏口号.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- and rain and domestic animals can no longer destroy the slogans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.80,1:26:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但又发生了新问题. 学生们能把砖偷走.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But a new problem has arised. The students can steal the bricks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.68,1:26:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}党委已对此表示严正关切. 当然,他们是对的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The Party comittee has expressed concerns over this. And of course they're right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.32,1:26:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人们必须能够 表达自己的感受, -\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}The people must be able to express their feelings, -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.20,1:26:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那是当然的.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- spontaneously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.92,1:26:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}自然自己动手.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Naturally and with their own hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.84,1:26:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你明白吗? - 是.谢谢.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}- Do you understand? - Yes. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.16,1:27:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在去吧.你全班都在校园等你.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Go now. Your class is waiting for you at the school yard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.56,1:27:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“稻堆堆得圆又圆,社员堆稻上了天. 撕片白云擦擦汗,凑上太阳抽根烟.”\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}"May the Campaign of Sowing and Harvesting be Crowned with Luck."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.16,1:27:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是老师,那有42个字母.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}But teacher, that's 42 letters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.00,1:27:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}用砖头还是石头,老师?\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}In brick or rocks, teacher?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.56,1:27:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}用石头.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}In rock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.40,1:27:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像以前一样.\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}Just like before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.08,1:28:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爱德华译制\N{\fs14\1c&H00FFFF&}English translation: x264{\r}

